  <lyrics>[V1]
 Tatitun ch'amapa
 Uñjamay jilata,
 Luratanacapaw
 Khananchasquistu. (Bis)
 
[C]
 Cristojj ch'amaniwa
 Khespiyañatac.
 Alajjpach marcasti
 Khespitanacatac
 Waquichatásqui. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Tatitun ch'amapajj
 Jumataquiraquiw.
 Catokarn jilata,
 Sum sarañatac. (Bis)
 
[V3]
 Munata jilata,
 Criston ch'amapampi
 Jupar arcañáni,
 Jan khepar cuttas. (Bis)
 
 </lyrics></song>